Project description

A Python package to read and write R RData and Rds filesinto/from pandas data frames. It does not need to have R or other externaldependencies installed.It is based on the C library librdata anda modified version of the cython wrapper jamovi-readstat.
Please visit out project home page for more information:
https://github.com/ofajardo/pyreadr
